name: No. 7 (Royal Red Over Deep Red)
description:
Work no. 7 of a collection of home made color field items.

This piece seems to glow from within, as if generating its own light, as if some mysterious space exists within it and the light from that space is emanating into this dimension through three red clouded glass.

They are created from a primal sensibility that talks about being and recalls the archaic presence of megalithic standing stones permeated with a deep ancient knowing.
